{"tid":1308402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求證]香港吉野家係咪真係由合興擁有經營權?","createTime":"2019-07-12T01:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T04:13:48.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f27072617b1316c54c596d6ca8602de03c82cedc","tid":1308402,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:27:12.000Z","msg":"求fact check<br />\n以下copy from合興個網<br />\n<br />\n發展史2012<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hophing.com/tch/aboutus/groupprofile.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hophing.com%2Ftch%2Faboutus%2Fgroupprofile.jsp&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0IhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=7d255e05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hophing.com/tch/aboutus/groupprofile.jsp</a><br />\n本集團將食油業務擴展至快餐業務, <span style=\"color: red;\">快餐業務在華北地區</span>以日本飯類快餐連鎖「吉野家」品牌及冰淇淋零售商「冰雪皇后」品牌營運。<br />\n<br />\n速食快餐業務<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hophing.com/tch/ourbusiness/fastfood.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hophing.com%2Ftch%2Fourbusiness%2Ffastfood.jsp&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0IhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=de06960a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hophing.com/tch/ourbusiness/fastfood.jsp</a><br />\n本集團在中國經營領先的快餐連鎖業務，擁有吉野家(Yoshinoya)及Dairy Queen快餐連鎖店舖。於二零一八年十二月三十一日在特許經營地區（<span style=\"color: red;\">包括北京市、天津市、河北省、遼寧省、黑龍江省、吉林省、河南省及內蒙古自治區</span>）內已開設357家吉野家店舖、173家Dairy Queen店舖和29家其他店舖。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hophing.com/tch/images/storenetwork.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hophing.com%2Ftch%2Fimages%2Fstorenetwork.jpg&h=d6ea9ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港係咪都係佢經營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ee615cff0856b050f645a716c4d795c56c65d7","tid":1308402,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T01:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2562050d1cc8bd6b0ca32ad1cd2ce35b4357437","tid":1